         <div type="edition">
            <note>The following text division is based on <bibl><ptr target="bm:Bachmann1893Lesestuecke"/>
            </bibl>
               and 
               <bibl>
                  <ptr target="bm:Spies1932Evagrius"/>
               </bibl>
            </note>
            <div type="textpart" xml:id="Treatise">
               <label>On the Eight Thoughts by Evagrius</label>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="TreatiseGluttony">
                  <label xml:lang="en">On the gluttonous belly <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ሥሡዕ፡ ከርሥ፡</foreign></label>
                  <label>Chapter One</label>
                  <note>A clear division into chapters, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አንቀጽ፡</foreign>, is provided only in some manuscripts. Likewise, only in some manuscripts is the chapter number added.</note>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="TreatiseAvarice">
                  <label>On Love of Gold and Silver <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ፍቅረ፡ ወርቅ፡ ወብሩር፡</foreign> </label>
                  <note>On Avarice</note>
                  <label>Chapter Two</label>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="TreatiseVainglory">
                  <label>On Vainglory <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ስብሐት፡ ብጡል፡</foreign></label>
                  <label>Chapter Three</label>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="TreatisePride">
                  <label>On Pride <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ትዕቢት፡</foreign> </label>
                  <label>Chapter Four</label>
            </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="TreatiseFornication">
                  <label>On the Unchaste <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ዘማዊ፡</foreign></label>
                  <note>On Fornication</note>
                  <label>Chapter Five</label>
                  <note>In some manuscripts Chapter 5 appears after Chapter 6.</note>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="TreatiseAnger">
                  <label>On Aversion and Anger <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ቍጥዓ፡ ወመዓት፡</foreign> </label>
                  <label>Chapter Six</label>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="TreatiseFear">
                  <label>On the Fearful <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ፈራህ፡</foreign></label>
                  <label>Chapter Seven</label>
               </div>
               
               <div type="textpart" xml:id="TreatiseRevange">
                  <label>On the Sickness of the Heart, the Shell of the Soul: Revenge <foreign xml:lang="gez">በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ልብ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ግላ፡ ነፍስ፡ በቀል፡</foreign></label>
                  <label>Chapter Eight</label>
               </div>
               <div type="textpart" subtype="colophon">  
                  <ab>በሰላም፡ ተተርጐመ፡ እምዓረቢ፡ ለግዕዝ። በመዋዕለ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ መፍቀሬ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ገላውዴዎስ። እምአመ፡ ነግሠ፡ በ፲ወ፫ዓመት፡ ስብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር: ወትረ፡ እስከ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</ab>
                  <note>The embedded colophon is taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmakm004">ʾƎndartā, Māy ʾAnbasā Dabra Gannat Kidāna Mǝḥrat, MAKM-004, f. 91rb-va</ref>.</note>
               </div>
               
               
            </div>
         </div>
